SQL_STMT_U.val: select MOV.Seq_nota, MAT.Cd_material, MAT.Descricao, MOV.Quantidade, iif((select 1 from TE_SERVICOXITEMNFE VIN (nolock) where VIN.Regime_Especial = :7 and VIN.Seq_Regime_Especial = :8 and VIN.Fornecedor = MOV.Cd_empresa and VIN.Serie = MOV.Serie and VIN.NF = MOV.Nf and VIN.UN = MOV.Uni_neg and VIN.Item_NF = MOV.Seq_nota) = 1, 1, 0), iif((select 1 from TE_SERVICOXITEMNFE VIN (nolock) where VIN.Regime_Especial = :7 and VIN.Seq_Regime_Especial = :8 and VIN.Fornecedor = MOV.Cd_empresa and VIN.Serie = MOV.Serie and VIN.NF = MOV.Nf and VIN.UN = MOV.Uni_neg and VIN.Item_NF <> MOV.Seq_nota) = 1, 0, 1), MOV.Quantidade - (select count(*) from TE_SERVICOXITEMNFE SXI (nolock) where SXI.Fornecedor = MOV.Cd_empresa and SXI.Serie = MOV.Serie and SXI.NF = MOV.Nf and SXI.UN = MOV.Uni_neg and SXI.Item_NF = MOV.Seq_nota) Qtde_sem_vinculo from /*ESMOVIME*/:1 MOV (nolock) inner join /*ESMATERI*/:2 MAT (nolock) on MAT.Cd_material = MOV.Cd_material where MOV.Tipo_movimento = 'E' and MOV.Cd_empresa = ':3' and MOV.Serie = ':4' and MOV.Nf = :5 and MOV.Uni_neg = ':6'
